            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>+ Exemplar. In nomine domini Dei et salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi.
                        Regnante piissimi domno nostro Liutprand et Hilprand vir excellentissimis
                        regibus, anni regni eorum vigensimo sexto et tertio, per indictione sexta,
                        mense februario; feliciter. Constat me <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Auripertus">Aurepert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Auti">Auti</name></persName> hac die vindedisse et vindedi,
                        tradedisse et tradedi tibi <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Iordanus"
                                >Iordanni</name></persName> viro venerabili <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbitero</rs> casa mea quem havire videor hic infra <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Casalini/fundamenta #Fruits/vegetables #Cisterns/pits"
                            ref="#places/4"><rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs></placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Casalini/fundamenta">fundamento</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >orto</rs>, seo <rs key="#Cisterns/pits">puteo</rs>; et posita est prope
                            <orgName>Sancto Georgio</orgName>: uno latere tenet in sepe <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Notary"><name ref="Radaldus">Raduald</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs> et caput tene in <rs
                            key="#Casalini/fundamenta">fondamento</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Casalini/fundamenta"><name
                                ref="Baruncio Belangonis">Barucioni Belongoni</name></persName>, et
                        alio latere tene in <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Fruits/vegetables"><name ref="Mamarianus"
                                >Mamariani</name></persName>; ut dixi, casa cum fundamento, curte,
                        orte vel puteo, omnia quem inivi havire visus sum in integro; unde mihi
                        nihil reservavi potestatem. Et suscepi ad te pretium placitum et in finito
                        capitulo adque in presentia solutus vigenti quinque soledus in auro; seo <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">petiola</rs> mea de terra mea quem havire
                        visus sum in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Cereals #Slave_labour #Slave" ref="#places/22"
                            >Flexo</placeName>, qui fuet de <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave"
                            >servo</rs> meo <persName key="#Slave"><name ref="Agnichis"
                                >Agnichis</name></persName>; ipsa petiola, quem modom esse <rs
                            key="#Cereals">seminata</rs> habeo, in integro, ita ut de meo qui supra
                        Auripert exivet dominio; his ipse suprascripta casa cum fundamento, curte,
                        orto vel puteo et in tua iam dicto Iordanni vel filius tuus heredem
                        transfundo esse potestatem possedendum, ut hab utierna die habeas, teneas
                        adque possedeas, tuoque dominio vindicis hac defendas. Et si forsitans
                        qualive tempore ego aut heredis meus te vel tuos heredem inquietare
                        molestare aut per quolivet ingenio subtrahere voluero, et a qualivet hominem
                        defensare menime potuero, promitto me iam nominato Aurepert clerico vel meus
                        heredis tibi Iordanni presbitero vel ad filios tuos heredem esse conponituro
                        ipsa res, unde agitur, meliorata, in dupla condicionem. Quam viro
                        vinditionis cartulam <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Alipert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> scribere rogavi. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>, die et regnum et indictione
                        suprascripta; feliciter. Signum + manus Aurepert clerico vinditori et
                        conservaturi. Signum + manus <persName
                            key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Carus"
                            >Cari</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Maurellus"
                                >Maurelli</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> testis. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">Causua[…</persName>
                        <persName>…]sari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti </rs>testis. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Alapert</name></persName> filius quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Sicualdus">Sicuald</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> testis. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Faolfus"
                                >Faolfu</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> testis. Ego Alipert
                        notarius huius cartule vinditionis post tradita et rovorata conplevi et
                        dedi. + Ego <persName key="#Writer #Other_clerics"><name ref="Richibrandus"
                                >Richiprandum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> in quantum cognuscere potui, hec
                        cartula fideliter exemplavi. </ab>
